abstract: Alastair Macaulay reviews performance by Liz Gerring Dance Company at Baryshnikov Arts Center.
snippet: Liz Gerring’s “She Dreams in Code,” at the Baryshnikov Arts Center, has several steps that stay powerfully in the memory.
